Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.37,0:22:30.59,DTB_OVA_EDjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\blur2}Hatasenu mama no yakusoku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:42.97,DTB_OVA_EDjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\blur2}Muda ni nagareta chi to namida ni somaru kanashii Game
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:47.06,DTB_OVA_EDjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\blur2}Oh where is my friend?
